        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Training our Prosecutors Act</b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2024 a Department of Justice grant program to provide training to state and local prosecutors. Further, it revises the program to include comprehensive continuing legal education in preventing and prosecuting violent crimes and crimes involving property destruction. </p>]]></text>
